{"tid":2400194,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"香港邊度有好食嘅桂花酒釀丸子食","createTime":"2021-02-08T17:38:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T02:44:32.000Z","uid":366189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"da32e2e02fb57ab8994214862a79bc454e3ab3d3","tid":2400194,"uid":366189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T17:38:41.000Z","msg":"之前覺得上海姥姥嘅幾好食 但依加藍的不了<br />\n喺屋企煮又冇出面整得好食 <br />\n啲丸子煮極都唔多煙韌<br />\n有冇推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />突然好想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2d60279294552c3af228aa3d29b1b9eaa0d61b7","tid":2400194,"uid":341722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da32e2e02fb57ab8994214862a79bc454e3ab3d3","tid":2400194,"uid":366189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T17:38:41.000Z","msg":"之前覺得上海姥姥嘅幾好食 但依加藍的不了<br />\n喺屋企煮又冇出面整得好食 <br />\n啲丸子煮極都唔多煙韌<br />\n有冇推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />突然好想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T17:59:17.000Z","msg":"屌 食過好多間 都覺得呢間特別好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己整其實要試多幾次粉同水既比例 係整到既<br />\n反而係個味 用悅和個桂花糖 硬係無出邊咁香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ae257ca8c284f8d7e194ebb7993292225b3b76f","tid":2400194,"uid":109573,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T18:32:11.000Z","msg":"好耐好耐之前自學過煮比鐘意既女仔食，雖然最後我同佢無一齊，但呢條配方應該幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n糯米粉 ：粘米粉 95 ：5 <br />\n<br />\n用叮暖既北海道360奶搓團，奶慢慢加，加到你搓到佢地變成一舊有彈性既面團就ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n搓成長條形，切粒，滾水落煲，煮到浮面，放冰水浸住。然後再煲一煲水，放冰糖/黃糖，煮滾放涼，用一個細碗裝起糖水，一個酒樓飯碗size既細碗糖水預落一湯匙酒釀，桂花蜜就跟自己口味落。<br />\n<br />\n酒釀唔好買香港牌子，十間九間有都酸到飛起。<br />\n而家HKTV mall直接買到台灣酒釀，怕酸可以再買桂花蜜。<br />\n<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91d2bed67d27f3adbb94737904a5d5e21f7de8d5","tid":2400194,"uid":366189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ae257ca8c284f8d7e194ebb7993292225b3b76f","tid":2400194,"uid":109573,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T18:32:11.000Z","msg":"好耐好耐之前自學過煮比鐘意既女仔食，雖然最後我同佢無一齊，但呢條配方應該幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n糯米粉 ：粘米粉 95 ：5 <br />\n<br />\n用叮暖既北海道360奶搓團，奶慢慢加，加到你搓到佢地變成一舊有彈性既面團就ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n搓成長條形，切粒，滾水落煲，煮到浮面，放冰水浸住。然後再煲一煲水，放冰糖/黃糖，煮滾放涼，用一個細碗裝起糖水，一個酒樓飯碗size既細碗糖水預落一湯匙酒釀，桂花蜜就跟自己口味落。<br />\n<br />\n酒釀唔好買香港牌子，十間九間有都酸到飛起。<br />\n而家HKTV mall直接買到台灣酒釀，怕酸可以再買桂花蜜。<br />\n<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T02:38:57.000Z","msg":"多謝ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />新年假試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5898590bc3fbaa26728a27c6992783d799deabe9","tid":2400194,"uid":366189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2d60279294552c3af228aa3d29b1b9eaa0d61b7","tid":2400194,"uid":341722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da32e2e02fb57ab8994214862a79bc454e3ab3d3","tid":2400194,"uid":366189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T17:38:41.000Z","msg":"之前覺得上海姥姥嘅幾好食 但依加藍的不了<br />\n喺屋企煮又冇出面整得好食 <br />\n啲丸子煮極都唔多煙韌<br />\n有冇推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />突然好想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T17:59:17.000Z","msg":"屌 食過好多間 都覺得呢間特別好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己整其實要試多幾次粉同水既比例 係整到既<br />\n反而係個味 用悅和個桂花糖 硬係無出邊咁香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T02:44:32.000Z","msg":"第一次食完就次次去親都會叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但好耐冇食過所以就快唔記得咩味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}